384 cases in last 21 days

There have been over 23 900 reported confirmed, probable, and suspected cases of EVD [Ebola virus disease] in Guinea, Liberia and Sierra Leone, with over 9800 reported deaths (outcomes for many cases are unknown). A total of 51 new confirmed cases were reported in Guinea, 0 in Liberia, and 81 in Sierra Leone in the 7 days to 1 Mar [2015].

